OL,3,CWhy does the deputy speaker oversee
OL,4,Cthe Budget rather than Sir Lindsay
OL,5,CHoyle?
OL,7,FThat role is currently held by Ghani,
OL,8,Fwho has served as both deputy speaker
OL,9,Fand chairman of Ways and Means since
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FShe is one of three deputy speakers,
OL,13,Falongside Judith Cummins and Caroline
OL,14,FNokes - each elected to distinct
OL,15,Fpositions within the speaker's team.
OL,17,FCummins serves as the first deputy
OL,18,Fchairman of Ways and Means, while
OL,19,FNokes serves as the second deputy
OL,20,Fchairman.
