OL,7,FWhat is the role of the deputy speaker?
OL,9,FThe role of the deputy is to assist
OL,10,Fthe speaker in chairing debates and
OL,11,Fperforming other parliamentary duties.
OL,13,FThe senior deputy speaker is elected
OL,14,Ffrom the opposite side of the House to
OL,15,Fthe speaker.
