OL,3,CWhy does the deputy speaker oversee
OL,4,Cthe Budget rather than Sir Lindsay
OL,5,CHoyle?
OL,7,FShe has previously held ministerial
OL,8,Fpositions in the Foreign, Commonwealth
OL,9,Fand Development Office and the
OL,10,FDepartment for Business and Trade.
